# PWC Backend

Flask API for the Poway Woman's Club website.

## Setup

```bash
cd pwc-backend
python3 -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
cp .env.example .env   # edit with your secrets
python main.py          # runs on http://localhost:5001
```

A default admin account is seeded on first run:
- username: `admin`
- password: `admin`

Change the password immediately.

## API Endpoints

### Auth (`/api/auth`)
| Method | Path | Auth | Description |
|--------|------|------|-------------|
| POST | `/register` | No | `{username, email, password}` |
| POST | `/login` | No | `{username, password}` (username or email) |
| POST | `/logout` | Yes | Ends session |
| GET | `/me` | Yes | Returns current user |
| POST | `/google` | No | `{code, redirect_uri}` — Google OAuth |

### Events (`/api/events`)
| Method | Path | Auth | Description |
|--------|------|------|-------------|
| GET | `/` | No | List events (`?upcoming=true`) |
| GET | `/:id` | No | Single event |
| POST | `/` | Admin | `{title, description, location, start_time, end_time}` |
| PUT | `/:id` | Admin | Update event |
| DELETE | `/:id` | Admin | Delete event |
| POST | `/:id/rsvp` | Yes | RSVP to event |
| DELETE | `/:id/rsvp` | Yes | Cancel RSVP |

### Blog (`/api/blog`)
| Method | Path | Auth | Description |
|--------|------|------|-------------|
| GET | `/posts` | No | List posts |
| GET | `/posts/:id` | No | Single post with comments |
| POST | `/posts` | Yes | `{title, body}` |
| PUT | `/posts/:id` | Author/Admin | Update post |
| DELETE | `/posts/:id` | Author/Admin | Delete post |
| POST | `/posts/:id/comments` | Yes | `{body}` |
| DELETE | `/comments/:id` | Author/Admin | Delete comment |

### Payments (`/api/payments`)
| Method | Path | Auth | Description |
|--------|------|------|-------------|
| POST | `/dues` | Yes | Pay membership (stub) |
| GET | `/history` | Yes | User's payment history |

### Admin (`/api/admin`)
| Method | Path | Auth | Description |
|--------|------|------|-------------|
| GET | `/stats` | Admin | Dashboard stats |
| GET | `/users` | Admin | List all users |
| PUT | `/users/:id` | Admin | Update role / membership |
| DELETE | `/users/:id` | Admin | Delete user |